<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11431] Add support of running from command line for &apos;hbase shell&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11431</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add support of running from command line for &apos;hbase shell&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now you can execute shell command from the bash like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  bin/hbase shell --exec=&apos;scan &quot;.META&quot;&apos; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The result can be piped to grep or other command.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
